snippet.title: ZOMBIES?!?! - Game of Thrones S1 Ep 8 Reaction
snippet.description:
Watch the unedited version here - https://www.suzylu.co.uk/ 
Suzy & Steejo react to Game of Thrones season 1. Game of Thrones is an American fantasy drama television series created by David Benioff and D. B. Weiss for HBO. It is an adaptation of A Song of Ice and Fire, a series of fantasy novels by George R. R. Martin, the first of which is A Game of Thrones.

Suzy - https://www.youtube.com/user/SuzyLuGME
Steejo - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTi180WJsC_0UTpCHEVYGrw

#GameofThrones
